---
import CaseStudyLayout from '../../layouts/CaseStudyLayout.astro';
---

<CaseStudyLayout
	name="PayLab Pro"
	category="FinTech"
	tagline="A comprehensive FinTech-as-a-Service platform enabling contractors to manage invoicing, payments, and client financing from one unified dashboard."
	gradient="from-blue-600 to-indigo-700"
	accentColor="text-blue-400"
	accentBg="bg-blue-500/10"
>
	<!-- Hero Visual -->
	<div slot="hero-visual" class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
		<div class="col-span-2 h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 p-6">
			<div class="h-3 w-24 bg-blue-200 rounded mb-4"></div>
			<div class="h-2 w-32 bg-blue-100 rounded mb-6"></div>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3">
				<div class="h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg"></div>
				<div class="h-16 bg-indigo-100 rounded-lg"></div>
				<div class="h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg"></div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 to-purple-50 rounded-xl border border-indigo-100 p-6 flex flex-col justify-between">
			<div class="h-3 w-16 bg-indigo-200 rounded"></div>
			<div class="text-3xl font-black text-indigo-600">$2.4M</div>
			<div class="h-2 w-20 bg-indigo-100 rounded"></div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- The Problem -->
	<section>
		<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-zinc-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">
			The <span class="text-blue-600">Problem</span>
		</h2>
		<div class="prose prose-lg prose-zinc max-w-none">
			<p class="text-zinc-500 text-lg leading-relaxed">
				Independent contractors across the home services industry were drowning in fragmented financial tools — spreadsheets for estimates, third-party apps for invoicing, manual bank transfers for payments, and zero visibility into project profitability. The average contractor used <strong class="text-zinc-700">5+ disconnected tools</strong> just to manage their finances, losing an estimated 8-12 hours per week on administrative overhead.
			</p>
			<p class="text-zinc-500 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-4">
				The pain was compounded by client financing — homeowners frequently wanted payment plans, but contractors had no easy way to offer them without complex third-party integrations that took weeks to set up and charged opaque fees.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- The Approach -->
	<section>
		<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-zinc-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">
			Our <span class="text-blue-600">Approach</span>
		</h2>
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-8">
			<div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white">
				<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
					<span class="text-blue-600 font-black text-sm">01</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-2">Discovery Sprint</h3>
				<p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">Two-week deep dive interviewing 30+ contractors to map every pain point in their financial workflow.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white">
				<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
					<span class="text-blue-600 font-black text-sm">02</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-2">API-First Architecture</h3>
				<p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">Designed a modular backend with Stripe Connect, Wisetack financing, and GoHighLevel CRM as pluggable services.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white">
				<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
					<span class="text-blue-600 font-black text-sm">03</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-2">Iterative Launch</h3>
				<p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">Shipped MVP in 6 weeks, then iterated weekly based on real contractor feedback and usage analytics.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- The Solution -->
	<section>
		<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-zinc-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">
			The <span class="text-blue-600">Solution</span>
		</h2>
		<p class="text-zinc-500 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
			PayLab Pro consolidates invoicing, payments, client financing, and CRM into a single dashboard purpose-built for contractors. The platform processes payments with transparent fee surcharging, offers one-click homeowner financing via embedded APIs, and provides real-time profitability dashboards.
		</p>
		<div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 p-6">
			<span class="text-xs font-bold text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 block">Tech Stack</span>
			<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
				{["React", "Astro", "Node.js", "Stripe Connect", "PostgreSQL", "Vercel", "Sentry", "Wisetack API"].map(tag => (
					<span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-white border border-zinc-200 text-zinc-600 text-xs font-semibold rounded-full">{tag}</span>
				))}
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Impact -->
	<div slot="impact" class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
		<div class="text-center">
			<div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-blue-400 mb-2">3x</div>
			<div class="text-zinc-400 text-sm font-medium">Faster invoicing</div>
		</div>
		<div class="text-center">
			<div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-blue-400 mb-2">40%</div>
			<div class="text-zinc-400 text-sm font-medium">Cost reduction</div>
		</div>
		<div class="text-center">
			<div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-blue-400 mb-2">$2.4M</div>
			<div class="text-zinc-400 text-sm font-medium">Processed in Q1</div>
		</div>
		<div class="text-center">
			<div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-blue-400 mb-2">92%</div>
			<div class="text-zinc-400 text-sm font-medium">User retention</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</CaseStudyLayout>
